<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;turuteenuse tegevusloa taotlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Application for employment services activity licence </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist t&ouml;&ouml;turuteenuseid osutav era&otilde;iguslik juriidiline isik ning f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tja on kohustatud taotlema tegevusluba seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest alates kuue kuu jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>Legal persons in private law and sole proprietors who provide employment services before entry into force of this Act are required to apply for activity licence within six months as of entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
