<eesti>Sotsiaalmaksuseaduse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of Social Tax Act </inglise>
<eesti>Sotsiaalmaksuseaduse (RT I 1998, 40, 611; 61, 982; 113/114, 1875 ja 1876; 1999, 29, 397; 71, 685; 82, 749; 87, 789; 88, 806; 97, 857; 101, 903) &sect; 6 l&otilde;ike 1 punkt 5 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>Clause 6 (1) 5) of the Social Tax Act (RT I 1998, 40, 611; 61, 982; 113/114, 1875 and 1876; 1999, 29, 397; 71, 685; 82, 749; 87, 789; 88, 806; 97, 857; 101, 903) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"5) t&ouml;&ouml;tu abiraha saava isiku eest." </eesti>
<inglise>"5) persons receiving unemployment benefit." </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 27. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 27. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu seaduse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of Republic of Estonia Employment Contracts Act </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu seaduse (RT 1992, 15/16, 241; 1993, 10, 150; RT I I993, 26, 441; 1995, 14, 170; 16, 228; 1996, 3, 57; 40, 773; 45, 850; 49, 953; 1997, 5/6, 32; 1998, 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 276; 60, 616; 2000, 25, 144; 51, 327; 57, 370; 102, 669; 2001, 17, 78; 42, 233) &sect; 88 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 88 of the Republic of Estonia Employment Contracts Act (RT 1992, 15/16, 241; 1993, 10, 150; RT I I993, 26, 441; 1995, 14, 170; 16, 228; 1996, 3, 57; 40, 773; 45, 850; 49, 953; 1997, 5/6, 32; 1998, 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 276; 60, 616; 2000, 25, 144; 51, 327; 57, 370; 102, 669; 2001, 17, 78; 42, 233) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 88. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 88. </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;h&otilde;iveametile t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu l&otilde;petamisest teatamine </eesti>
<inglise>Notice to employment office of termination of employment contract </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;lepingu l&otilde;petamisel ettev&otilde;tte, asutuse v&otilde;i organisatsiooni likvideerimise v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tajate koondamise t&otilde;ttu on t&ouml;&ouml;andja kohustatud esitama andmed vabanevate t&ouml;&ouml;tajate kohta t&ouml;&ouml;taja elukohaj&auml;rgsele t&ouml;&ouml;h&otilde;iveametile hiljemalt j&auml;rgmisel p&auml;eval, kui ta on teatanud t&ouml;&ouml;tajale t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu l&otilde;petamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon termination of employment contracts due to the liquidation of an enterprise, agency or organisation, or the lay-off of employees, the employer is required to submit information regarding the released employees to the employment office of residence of the employees not later than on the following day after the employer notifies the employees of termination of the employment contracts. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui t&ouml;&ouml;leping l&otilde;petatakse t&ouml;&ouml;tajatega t&ouml;&ouml;andaja pankroti v&auml;ljakuulutamisel, esitab t&ouml;&ouml;andja t&ouml;&ouml;tajate kohta andmed t&ouml;&ouml;h&otilde;iveametile t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu l&otilde;petamisele j&auml;rgneval p&auml;eval." </eesti>
<inglise>If employment contracts are terminated with employees upon the declaration of bankruptcy of the employer, the employer shall submit information regarding the employees to the employment office on the date following termination of the employment contracts." </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 28. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 28. </inglise>
